[SN]TITLE[SN]
Michael Onovwigun: Southport sign former Chesterfield midfielder

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Southport have signed former Chesterfield and Gateshead midfielder Michael Onovwigun.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 20-year-old began his career at Brentford, playing more than 50 games for the London club's youth team.
He made his Football League debut for Chesterfield in 2014-15 and last season appeared three times in the National League in a loan spell at Gateshead.
Onovwigun goes straight into the Southport squad for Saturday's away game at Aldershot.
